 src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efbb5f84ce6ac97a1e3f4907a9849bec1ef7328","tid":1016753,"uid":161160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce7566a92104b06ee04002f9b5918b769e511340","tid":1016753,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f2e15fff06229845ec1c10be3cc60ef17559862","tid":1016753,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81d793c0639f58bf047d2c7c33b1d358eed8cb05","tid":1016753,"uid":51250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:35:09.000Z","msg":"繁時59由龍門居去美孚/荔枝角，半個鐘得？<br />\n行落地鐵站轉車等車都又起碼浪費5-10分鐘<br />\n仲要企足全程"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:40:31.000Z","msg":"59&gt; 荔枝角正常都35分鐘到<br />\n荔枝角站 行一分鐘就到地鐵站<br />\n繁時地鐵多班 耐極都係兩分鐘<br />\n太子多數吉車到 一落就會上到<br />\n你試一日就知有幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n龍門居門車兜屯碼=地鐵由荔枝角去到牛頭角<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:46:42.000Z","msg":"35+30都65，轉車用5分鐘，都70分鐘，又要行上行落，不了<br />\n<br />\n我唔係觀塘返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T21:12:39.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n寧願一程坐到尾"},{"pid":"4c09a9711c464a01107aacbe0b8c964577226766","tid":1016753,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n龍門居小食冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}